snippet.title: Minnesota 4K Autumn - Experience the Vibrant Fall Colors and Serene Lakes - Relaxing Piano
snippet.description:
Minnesota 4K Autumn - Experience the Vibrant Fall Colors and Serene Lakes - Relaxing Piano

Minnesota in autumn transforms into a vibrant tapestry of color, with its forests bursting into shades of gold, red, and orange. The crisp, cool air enhances the beauty of the changing leaves, particularly around the scenic North Shore along Lake Superior. The state's many lakes mirror the stunning fall foliage, creating picturesque reflections. Scenic drives, especially along the Great River Road and through state parks like Itasca and Gooseberry Falls, showcase Minnesota‚Äôs autumn brilliance. Wildlife becomes more visible, and the quiet rustling of leaves creates a peaceful, serene atmosphere perfect for outdoor adventures.

snippet.title: Incredible Fall Foliage of New England from Above in 8K - Autumn Ambient Drone Film (2021)
snippet.description:
This amazing 8K nature relax video will bring you to the mesmerizing virtual fly above the fall foliage of New England! Watch the stunning beauty of autumn nature with calming light instrumental music. Enjoy the bright variety of colors while flying above Hew Hampshire, Massachusetts, and Connecticut states. Here in this wonderful video, you will be able to touch the astonishing golden sea of foliage surrounding the deep blue eyes of water. Take a comfortable position, play this amazing 8K nature video and let your imagination take you on the best relaxing journey! This video was filmed by our nature filmmaker Roman Khomlyak using a 6K drone EVO II Pro in 2021. 
Enjoy the beauty of autumn scenery of New England with us (00:00:00): 
Everett Lake Dam, New Hampshire 00:13:06
Plymouth, New Hampshire 00:17:39
Campton, New Hampshire 00:20:50
Waterville Valley, new Hampshire 00:27:15
Kent Falls State Park, Connecticut 01:06:35
Heublein Tower, Connecticut 01:09:42
Meddletown, Connecticut 01;20:23

We would like to express our thankfulness to Autel Robotics for presenting us with a great drone 6K EVO II Pro. You can check their products here: https://www.autelrobotics.com/

Video from: New England, USA
Video title: New England`s Fall Foliage - 2021 View From Above
Time of filming: Autumn 2021
Equipment used: 6K drone EVO II Pro
Video type: Drone Video ‚Äì Nature Relax Video
Video resolution: 8K
Producer: Roman Khomlyak, Pro Art Inc
Cinematographer: Roman Khomlyak
Editor and colorist: Stanislav Goncharuk
Supervising editor: Anatolii Pylypenko
Music selection:  Anatolii Pylypenko

The fall foliage period in New England averages from mid-September to mid-November. It is at this time that plain green landscapes turn into a variety of colors! The peak of brightness usually falls in October and this time strikes the eyes of everyone who sees it. In New England, a large percentage of trees produce a pigment known as Anthocyanin, which results in brilliant reds and purples commonly seen around this time.

Try this 8K aerial video as a screensaver for your HDTV. Feel how the pleasant sounds of music and the stunning colors of autumn turn the dullness of dank everyday life into a delightful romantic atmosphere around you. Relax when you fly over the woods and parks of New England with the drone. Admire the riot of colors from a bird's eye view and discard all negativity from your thoughts!
